		)

			[SumDoanh_Thu],
			350,

			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

	'Ket Qua KD'[Ngày]
